text: Odd-Even Bustnes (born 17 November 1969) is a Norwegian rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Norway Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Hamar
